# Personal Finance CLI

A simple command-line interface for managing personal finances.

## Features
- Expense tracking
- Budget management
- Savings goals
- Data persistence (stored in `~/.personal_finance_data`)

## Installation

```bash
pip install personal_finance_cli
```

## Usage

Run the application:

```bash
personal-finance
```
